  "front_page_blocks_3_two_columns_1_text": "<h2>Our<span class=\"dark_text\"> model-based </span>approach to testing</h2>\r\nBoozang makes it easy to build powerful and maintainable end-to-end tests using a model-based visual interface. Instead of writing scripts, users create flows by linking test modules that represent UI actions and API calls.\r\n\r\nThis modular approach improves test reusability and allows teams to quickly adapt to changes without rewriting everything. You can visualize your application’s logic and manage test data – all from within your browser.\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>Visualize the structure of your application and test flows</li>\r\n \t<li>Create reusable building blocks that scale with your development</li>\r\n \t<li>Maintain stability even in fast-changing, complex systems</li>\r\n</ul>",
  "front_page_blocks_3_two_columns_1_link": "a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"More about model-based testing\";s:3:\"url\";s:62:\"https://docs.boozang.com/docs/model-based-testing/introduction\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}",
